data_table.description: Sample ID, analyte type, body site where sample was obtained, and tumor status of sample of participants with or without cardiovascular diseases and involved in the "NHLBI TOPMed: Trans-Omics for Precision Medicine (TOPMed) Whole Genome Sequencing Project: ARIC" project.

variable.name: BODY_SITE
variable.description: Body site where sample was collected

variable.name: SEQUENCING_CENTER
variable.description: Name of the center which conducted sequencing

variable.name: Study_Name
variable.description: TOPMed-assigned short study name (1:1 with TOPMed phs number)

variable.name: VTE_TYPE
variable.comment: Blank for subjects not in VTE case or comparison groups (e.g., afib cases)
